to their communities.

00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:41.570
And 98% identified their
public library experiences

00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:44.330
as "very" or "mostly" positive.

00:13:44.330 --> 00:13:46.660
Another Pew study found 94%

00:13:46.660 --> 00:13:50.090
