search term, I found thousands

00:15:04.620 --> 00:15:07.710
of voices in letters to the
editor, thousands more quoted

00:15:07.710 --> 00:15:10.480
in stories reporters wrote
about local libraries.

00:15:10.480 --> 00:15:14.030
And almost all of those
newspapers I read here

00:15:14.030 --> 00:15:15.610
in the Library of Congress.

00:15:15.610 --> 00:15:18.750
Some of you watched me
look at those databases.

00:15:18.750 --> 00:15:22.360
