that came when I concentrated

00:33:29.910 --> 00:33:33.620
on solving a problem, and
everything else faded out."

00:33:33.620 --> 00:33:36.810
Her reading that summer,
she admitted, was her solace

00:33:36.810 --> 00:33:41.010
and only distraction that got
her through this time of trouble.

00:33:41.010 --> 00:33:47.380 position:56%
All these anecdotes point to the
power of printed commonplace stories

00:33:47.380 --> 00:33:49.920
to change people's lives.

00:33:49.920 --> 00:33:53.210
But stories reside in
all cultural media.

00:33:53.210 --> 00:33:56.800
