on a set of stories acceptable

00:37:10.300 --> 00:37:12.800
to a majority of community members

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:17.400
that contained messages they
wanted to hear, read, and view.

00:37:17.400 --> 00:37:20.630
The latest public library
circulation statistics I'll detail

00:37:20.630 --> 00:37:23.540 position:56%
in a minute show that they still do.

00:37:23.540 --> 00:37:26.730
Reading scholars have clearly
demonstrated the capacity

00:37:26.730 --> 00:37:30.800
