meaning relevant to their own lives.

00:37:44.920 --> 00:37:46.960
Because readers can control it,

00:37:46.960 --> 00:37:51.870
the act of reading stories becomes
dependably pleasurable, empowering,

00:37:51.870 --> 00:37:54.910
intellectually stimulating,
and socially bonding.

00:37:54.910 --> 00:37:57.500
And it's in the act of
reading stories that social

00:37:57.500 --> 00:38:00.970
and cultural acts of
defiance can take place.

00:38:00.970 --> 00:38:03.680
If cultural authorities
-- like H.L. Mencken --

00:38:03.680 --> 00:38:06.390
lack the power to check
voluntary reading

00:38:06.390 --> 00:38:10.380
