00:38:22.390 --> 00:38:24.930
and stories, as is
evident from Seeger's,

00:38:24.930 --> 00:38:27.350
Reagan's, and Winfrey's remarks.

00:38:27.350 --> 00:38:29.640
Sometimes they don't, however.

00:38:29.640 --> 00:38:35.870
Let's see -- In October of 1912,

00:38:35.870 --> 00:38:39.970
