00:41:05.220 --> 00:41:06.520
They were wrong.

00:41:06.520 --> 00:41:07.820
Dead wrong.

00:41:07.820 --> 00:41:12.490
In 2012, which is the last year for
which we have national statistics,

00:41:12.490 --> 00:41:15.630
the United States had more
public libraries than ever --

00:41:15.630 --> 00:41:20.880
17,219, including branches
and bookmobiles.

00:41:20.880 --> 00:41:23.680
And over 3,000 more than the number

00:41:23.680 --> 00:41:28.090
