in the country.

00:41:28.090 --> 00:41:34.190
While the number of visits
declined slightly in 2012 from 1.52

00:41:34.190 --> 00:41:37.370
to 1.5 billion -- bear in mind,

00:41:37.370 --> 00:41:41.140
though the recession forced
libraries to reduce hours by 2%,

00:41:41.140 --> 00:41:43.940
and more patrons were
downloading library e-books

00:41:43.940 --> 00:41:45.670
from their home computers,

00:41:45.670 --> 00:41:49.470
the decade nonetheless
showed a 21% increase.

00:41:49.470 --> 00:41:53.770 position:56%
That same year, 93 million Americans
attended a public library program.

00:41:53.770 --> 00:41:59.380
A one-year increase of 4%, and
an eight-year increase of 38%.

00:41:59.380 --> 00:42:01.880
Sixty-five million
attendees were children,

00:42:01.880 --> 00:42:04.770
a nearly 4% increase
from the previous year.

00:42:04.770 --> 00:42:08.210
And a 24%increase from
