useful simulation.

00:44:08.880 --> 00:44:13.930 position:56%
Because negotiating the social world
effectively is extremely tricky,

00:44:13.930 --> 00:44:18.170
requiring us to weigh up
myriad interacting instances

00:44:18.170 --> 00:44:19.870
of cause and effect.

00:44:19.870 --> 00:44:22.900
Just as computer simulations
can help us get to grips

00:44:22.900 --> 00:44:27.450
with complex scientific
problems, so novels, stories,

00:44:27.450 --> 00:44:32.070
