contact American public libraries

00:44:40.870 --> 00:44:45.540
make possible in so many ways
enables users to live longer,

00:44:45.540 --> 00:44:49.670
happier, and healthier
lives than non-users.

00:44:49.670 --> 00:44:52.540
This is a researchable question.

00:44:52.540 --> 00:44:55.220
And if they do, why?

00:44:55.220 --> 00:44:58.830
Answering that question
requires librarianship

00:44:58.830 --> 00:45:04.010 position:56%
to expand way beyond its traditional
focus on information access in order

00:45:04.010 --> 00:45:07.400
to explore the community
building and personal benefits

00:45:07.400 --> 00:45:12.680
that public libraries place in
the sociability that reading,

00:45:12.680 --> 00:45:15.220
viewing, and listening fosters.

00:45:15.220 --> 00:45:19.870
For generations now, adolescent
series fiction and adult westerns,

00:45:19.870 --> 00:45:23.710
romances, horror, and science
fiction novels have driven public

00:45:23.710 --> 00:45:25.130
library circulation.

00:45:25.130 --> 00:45:26.430
And they still do.

00:45:26.430 --> 00:45:29.880
Through commonplace stories
like these that they circulate

00:45:29.880 --> 00:45:33.860
by the billions, American public
libraries have helped empower,

00:45:33.860 --> 00:45:36.100
inform, intellectually stimulate,

00:45:36.100 --> 00:45:38.760
and inspire their readers,
viewers and listeners.

00:45:38.760 --> 00:45:41.590
Just like they did for
Pete Seeger, Ronald Reagan,

00:45:41.590 --> 00:45:44.230
Oprah Winfrey, and Sonia Sotomayor.

00:45:44.230 --> 00:45:48.350
Tens of thousands of spaces they
make available to their patrons,

00:45:48.350 --> 00:45:52.360
they have helped construct
community in multiple positive ways

00:45:52.360 --> 00:45:55.660 position:56%
through the billions of face-to-face
encounters they nurture.

00:45:55.660 --> 00:46:00.520
Just like they did for Martin
Luther King Jr. and Conrad Cheek.

00:46:00.520 --> 00:46:03.800
In my lifetime of research
into American library history,

00:46:03.800 --> 00:46:06.220
I've read thousands
of statements like,

